```r
quartiles <- quantile(data$Followers, probs = c( 0.25, 0.75 ))

iqr <- IQR(data$Followers)

lower_outliers <- quartiles[1] - 1.5*iqr
upper_outliers <- quartiles[2] + 1.5*iqr

data_cleaned <- filter(data, data$Followers < upper_outliers)
all_data_cleaned <- filter(all_data, all_data$Followers < upper_outliers)

glimpse(data_cleaned)
Rows: 360
Columns: 2
$ ig_name   <chr> "ace.vav", "ahra.view", "a_young91", "hv_alice", "ajol_llama", "arang_official_md", "tahiti__ari", "ye._.vely618", …
$ Followers <dbl> 335439, 12342, 10479, 11135, 5519743, 17749, 30965, 1857972, 718784, 541344, 442087, 313078, 71558, 10703, 2703891,…
```r
data_length <- data_cleaned %>% mutate( length = nchar(ig_name) )

ggplot (data_length) +
  aes ( y = Followers, 
        x = length) +
  geom_point()

  aes ( y = Followers, 
        x = number_of_numbers) +

#contains_group_name <- str_detect(data_cleaned$ig_name, tolower(all_data_cleaned$Group))
#contains_group_name <- tibble(as.numeric(contains_group_name))

#Reformat names: 
#group_name_no_punctuations <- str_replace_all((all_data_cleaned$Group), "[[:punct:]]", "")

library(stringr)

data_texts <- data %>% mutate(
  
  contains_official = str_count(data$ig_name, "official"),
  contains_group_name = str_detect(data$ig_name, tolower(str_replace_all((data$Group), "[[:punct:]]", ""))),
  contains_stage_name = str_detect(data$ig_name, tolower(str_replace_all((data$Stage.Name), " ", "")))
 
   )

ggplot(data_texts) + 
  aes (x = Followers, y = contains_group_name, fill = contains_group_name, alpha = 0.5) +
  geom_boxplot(width = 0.4) +
  scale_x_continuous(trans='log2') +
  theme_dark() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.x = element_blank(),
        legend.position = "none") 



ggplot(data_texts) + 
  aes (x = Followers, 
      fill = contains_stage_name) +
  geom_histogram()
